  abilityName: Punitive Stroke
  description: "Make a melee Attack against a known liar.\nGet +d10 to the Attack,
    ignoring armour .\nPASSION - Honesty\nRestore SPI when you tell the truth where
    a\nlie might be more beneficial.\nKNIGHTED BY...\nThe Rotted Seer\nVIG 7, CLA
    5, SPI 11, 2 GD\n\u2022 Their withered touch is only contagious if\nthey will
    it.\n\u2022 Sees the way to live on through any\namount of physical decay.\n\u2022
    Wants to become even more rotten, filthy,\nand diseased.\nA pact to uphold truth
    and fact\nOn lies the false lay brake and cracked\nTrue Knight\nSYMBOL OF THE
    TRUTH\nTrigger Effect\n1 Lying to you about\ntheir identity Golden glow\n2 Giving
    false witness\nto you Turns cold\n3 Giving you malicious\nadvice Gentle hum\n4
    Lying while bearing\nthe shield Fragrant aroma\n5 Omitting key\ninformation to
    you Distant birdcall\n6 Lying to you about\ntheir intent Loud clang\nPerson:
    Wandering old coot ~ Name: Senara ~ Characteristic: Thunderous voice\nObject:
    Grey lantern ~ Beast: Smiling fox ~ State: Feasting ~ Theme: Sleep\n1\n1\nThe"
